title: Religion
comment: Religious people may have a problem with this as it 'plays God'.

title: Who regulates this?
comment: Would this be a government approved piece of technology?

title: Could be used in an irresponsible way
comment: People could jeopardise their long term health by using this far too much or too little.

title: Goes against nature
comment: Humans are not supposed to potentially stay up for days on end partying or studying. This could make you seriously unwell. You could also argue that people sleep when they need to and this shouldn't be artificially altered.

title: Not relevant to me personally
comment: I have no issues sleeping so from a selfish point of view it wouldn't help me!
